WEBVTT

00:00:02.002 --> 00:00:05.406
[Got it]

00:00:09.334 --> 00:00:10.534
Khun!

00:00:10.534 --> 00:00:12.545
Stella!

00:00:17.901 --> 00:00:19.300
Ugh, seriously?

00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:21.821
What's going on between them?

00:00:43.701 --> 00:00:45.445
Hello.

00:00:45.445 --> 00:00:47.180
You can't even hold your liquor.

00:00:47.180 --> 00:00:49.449
Why drink so much?

00:00:51.334 --> 00:00:53.300
You live pretty far, too.

00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:55.169
Don't drink too much next time.

00:00:57.567 --> 00:01:00.727
Thanks for getting me home that night.

00:01:01.962 --> 00:01:03.400
That's it?

00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:04.459
What?

00:01:04.459 --> 00:01:08.033
You were drooling like crazy in your sleep.

00:01:08.033 --> 00:01:10.335
Ruined my pants.

00:01:12.367 --> 00:01:14.481
Let's be more careful next time.

00:01:16.743 --> 00:01:18.786
I'll take that.

00:01:36.305 --> 00:01:38.640
Stop!

00:01:41.351 --> 00:01:43.108
Do it again.

00:01:44.730 --> 00:01:46.315
Just you.

00:01:47.024 --> 00:01:49.176
Five, six, seven, eight.

00:01:49.176 --> 00:01:54.447
One, two, three, four, five, six.

00:01:56.167 --> 00:01:57.931
What are you doing?

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:02.039
You keep getting it wrong!

00:02:02.039 --> 00:02:03.767
I'm sorry, sir.

00:02:03.767 --> 00:02:06.460
It isn't just Jae Min, honestly.

00:02:06.460 --> 00:02:08.966
It's all of you.

00:02:08.966 --> 00:02:12.885
Hyun Jae's the only one keeping up here.

00:02:12.885 --> 00:02:14.901
You all want to drag him down?

00:02:14.901 --> 00:02:16.136
Huh?

00:02:16.136 --> 00:02:18.222
Riding on his coattails?

00:02:18.222 --> 00:02:21.108
You should be ashamed.

00:02:21.108 --> 00:02:24.122
And you're the worst of them, Shin Jae Min.

00:02:24.122 --> 00:02:26.772
Don't you think you're holding everyone back?

00:02:26.772 --> 00:02:30.017
I'm more than ten years older than you,
and I practice every day.

00:02:30.017 --> 00:02:33.053
What's your excuse?

00:02:33.053 --> 00:02:34.867
Huh?

00:02:35.864 --> 00:02:38.420
Say something.

00:02:43.167 --> 00:02:44.865
You made it.

00:02:44.865 --> 00:02:47.209
Grab a seat over there.

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:54.806
- Must be nice. All by himself.
- Right?

00:02:54.806 --> 00:02:56.566
You'd think he already debuted.

00:02:56.566 --> 00:02:59.626
He did debut, though.

00:02:59.626 --> 00:03:01.793
Hey, from the top.

00:03:20.826 --> 00:03:22.818
Stop!

00:03:29.168 --> 00:03:31.037
Did you just stop on your own?

00:03:31.037 --> 00:03:33.777
- No, it's not that...
- Hey!

00:03:33.777 --> 00:03:35.424
You think this is a joke?

00:03:35.424 --> 00:03:38.518
Who said you could break the flow?

00:03:38.518 --> 00:03:40.474
I'm sorry.

00:03:42.100 --> 00:03:43.969
Again.

00:03:45.534 --> 00:03:47.479
Focus.

00:03:56.820 --> 00:04:00.092
What I went over today,
have it down by tomorrow.

00:04:00.092 --> 00:04:02.432
Am I making myself clear?

00:04:02.432 --> 00:04:04.010
Practice at two tomorrow.

00:04:04.010 --> 00:04:05.510
That's it.

00:04:06.767 --> 00:04:08.934
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:04:13.212 --> 00:04:15.212
What is it?

00:04:34.908 --> 00:04:38.543
Try counting the beat a different way.

00:04:39.334 --> 00:04:40.601
How?

00:04:40.601 --> 00:04:42.315
You keep missing this part

00:04:42.315 --> 00:04:46.534
because you're counting it as one,

00:04:46.534 --> 00:04:49.923
but connect it

00:04:49.923 --> 00:04:53.091
and count it as two instead.

00:04:53.091 --> 00:04:56.541
One, two...

00:04:59.742 --> 00:05:01.601
- There it is!
- See?

00:05:01.601 --> 00:05:03.234
It's not your fault.

00:05:03.234 --> 00:05:06.167
He just doesn't know how to teach.

00:05:06.167 --> 00:05:08.100
No.

00:05:08.100 --> 00:05:10.701
I just couldn't keep up.

00:05:10.701 --> 00:05:13.567
If someone can't keep up,
the teacher should teach better,

00:05:13.567 --> 00:05:15.607
not blame them.

00:05:15.607 --> 00:05:18.235
What a massive jerk.

00:05:23.434 --> 00:05:27.928
Why do people learn curse words so fast?

00:05:27.928 --> 00:05:30.067
Hell if I know.

00:05:32.467 --> 00:05:34.277
Heading out?

00:05:34.277 --> 00:05:36.462
No, I want to keep practicing.

00:05:36.462 --> 00:05:38.046
It's late. You go ahead.

00:05:38.046 --> 00:05:40.107
That actually would help me.

00:05:40.107 --> 00:05:44.044
I can't focus with you here.

00:05:44.044 --> 00:05:46.505
Why do you work so hard?

00:05:48.682 --> 00:05:50.885
Because I want to do it...

00:05:50.885 --> 00:05:52.506
with you.

00:06:03.614 --> 00:06:06.408
You all want to drag him down? Huh?

00:06:06.408 --> 00:06:08.468
You're free to walk away,

00:06:08.468 --> 00:06:11.604
but more people are
rooting for you than you think.

00:06:14.474 --> 00:06:16.269
[Mom]

00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:25.500
Mom.

00:06:28.534 --> 00:06:30.108
Yeah.

00:06:31.300 --> 00:06:32.784
Yeah.

00:06:35.145 --> 00:06:37.631
Mom, I...

00:06:37.631 --> 00:06:40.236
Let me try just one more time.

00:07:54.927 --> 00:07:56.276
Guess a big company doesn't mean much.

00:07:56.276 --> 00:07:58.645
Look at this filthy practice room.

00:07:58.645 --> 00:08:01.481
The practice room at our old agency
used to be so clean...

00:08:01.481 --> 00:08:03.483
Hyun Jae's so lucky.

00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:06.353
Off on a business trip with the boss,
skipping practice.

00:08:06.353 --> 00:08:08.073
So jealous.

00:08:08.701 --> 00:08:11.501
Hey, if you're so jealous,
step up and debut already.

00:08:11.501 --> 00:08:14.260
They have to pick me first.

00:08:18.298 --> 00:08:20.769
[Every day at 4 AM]

00:09:12.678 --> 00:09:15.020
You don't drink that, do you?

00:09:20.143 --> 00:09:22.020
You're right.

00:09:31.334 --> 00:09:33.071
Warm.

00:09:38.467 --> 00:09:40.518
See you around.

00:09:54.868 --> 00:09:56.534
Soft.

00:09:58.932 --> 00:10:00.839
See you around.

00:10:04.267 --> 00:10:06.827
Hey! That's cheating!

00:10:17.701 --> 00:10:18.718
That's awesome.

00:10:18.718 --> 00:10:20.537
Khun. It's all thanks to you.

00:10:20.537 --> 00:10:22.207
Thank you.

00:10:29.129 --> 00:10:32.610
You're the one who works hard.

00:10:34.009 --> 00:10:35.968
Khun.

00:10:35.968 --> 00:10:38.109
Do you have plans?

00:10:54.434 --> 00:10:56.134
You like it?

00:10:56.789 --> 00:10:58.289
Yeah.

00:10:58.909 --> 00:11:02.595
Well, this is our first time
going out for drinks together.

00:11:02.595 --> 00:11:05.256
We were supposed to hit all the nice spots.

00:11:18.734 --> 00:11:23.167
Dancing has been my problem
since day one as a trainee.

00:11:23.167 --> 00:11:25.749
Years in, and it's still hard.

00:11:26.382 --> 00:11:28.506
Were you always good?

00:11:30.107 --> 00:11:31.942
Of course.

00:11:31.942 --> 00:11:33.969
Good at singing too?

00:11:35.696 --> 00:11:37.469
Of course.

00:11:38.376 --> 00:11:39.832
Life's so unfair.

00:11:39.832 --> 00:11:42.934
You sing, you dance, you write songs.

00:11:42.934 --> 00:11:45.276
Is there anything you can't do?

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.821
Curious?

00:11:52.378 --> 00:11:55.815
Stick around and you might find out.

00:12:11.331 --> 00:12:13.829
[Stella: Where are you?]

00:12:20.501 --> 00:12:22.253
Stella!

00:12:39.868 --> 00:12:41.606
Jae Min.

00:12:43.267 --> 00:12:45.731
I want you to meet someone.

00:13:05.801 --> 00:13:08.754
Shin Jae Min, you idiot.

00:13:09.567 --> 00:13:12.491
Hold on! Don't come in. I mean it!

00:13:13.617 --> 00:13:15.328
- Huh?
- Stayed out again?

00:13:15.328 --> 00:13:17.117
Seriously, who are you seeing?

00:13:17.117 --> 00:13:19.234
It's not like that.

00:13:19.234 --> 00:13:21.926
What's going on with you and Stella...

00:13:23.345 --> 00:13:25.405
The fans want to see the two of you.

00:13:25.405 --> 00:13:27.098
So we'll shoot some videos with just you two.

00:13:27.098 --> 00:13:28.608
For the making-of video
we're filming this time...

00:13:28.608 --> 00:13:31.344
Why don't you two do it together?
What do you think?

00:13:31.344 --> 00:13:32.612
Good morning!

00:13:32.612 --> 00:13:34.573
Time to head to the shoot.